{"data":[{"id":562859753,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"4d5ac508d89d0be22389f1dacabd0a90","url_token":"virbianium","name":"而后 乃今培风","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b5d0eb929c513a4b6cc65f1be8a8a3a1_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b5d0eb929c513a4b6cc65f1be8a8a3a1_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/4d5ac508d89d0be22389f1dacabd0a90","user_type":"people","headline":"一个想成为理论物理学家，也知道自己可能在做梦但为之奋斗的青年。","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":8,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562859753","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546154647,"updated_time":1546154647,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"comment_count":8,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e答主和题主有点像，也想考清北。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果说大多数人物理天赋是1.0，那我可能在1.5~2.0之间，IPhO、APhO国家队应该有3.0+，而且他们还刻苦训练。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e读了高中，知道了五大竞赛这回事。仗着初中物理水平压某一线城市的二，三线初中全级同学一头，兴冲冲地入了坑，发现连入门级的物竞题都做不出来。经过这几个月的学习下来，我总算是懂了点皮毛。而且总结出一个规律。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003ci\u003e高考是通向好大学的最快最简单最轻松途径。\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e像竞赛这种，检测单科水平的比赛，许多人认为那是捷径，其实不然，它需要的综合水平，比高考更高。而参加竞赛去了清北的，90%以上都是能裸分清北的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e只有真正接触过竞赛的，才会明白竞赛党的苦和累，还有竞赛的难。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e还有学习数学物理之路的漫长。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e前路是一座又一座山。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e而证明哥德巴赫猜想，其难度比竞赛更高百倍，这更不是种捷径，是一个无底洞。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e他会吞掉你无穷无尽的时间，无穷无尽的精力。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这是种赌博，不要投入太多在里面，避免毁灭性的失败。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果题主真的和哥德巴赫猜想有不解之缘，想去北大清华只是流于表面的原因，那么还是选择扎扎实实学好课内知识，考上一所好的大学，努力提升自己的数学水平，等到水平真的达到那种境界的时候，再专攻哥德巴赫猜想。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e可能明年的CPhO预赛都过不去的准物竞选手如实说：）\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"答主和题主有点像，也想考清北。如果说大多数人物理天赋是1.0，那我可能在1.5~2.0之间，IPhO、APhO国家队应该有3.0+，而且他们还刻苦训练。读了高中，知道了五大竞赛这回事。仗着初中物理水平压某一线城市的二，三线初中全级同学一头，兴冲冲地入了坑，发现…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=304\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Cr